NPC Shield Use
    Events
        Unit - A unit Is attacked
    Conditions
        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
            Conditions
                (Level of Shield Block (50) for (Triggering unit)) Greater than 0
                (Level of Shield Block (75) for (Triggering unit)) Greater than 0
                (Level of Shield Block (100) for (Triggering unit)) Greater than 0
        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
            Conditions
                (Unit-type of (Triggering unit)) Equal to Rogue (Companion)
                (Unit-type of (Triggering unit)) Equal to Tauren Warrior (Companion)
                (Unit-type of (Triggering unit)) Equal to Paladin (Companion)
                (Unit-type of (Triggering unit)) Equal to Engineer
    Actions
        -------- Restoshaman, Warlock excluded --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (Random integer number between 1 and 3) Equal to 1
            Then - Actions
                -------- Shield Block usage --------
                Unit - Order (Attacked unit) to Orc Troll Berserker - Berserk.
            Else - Actions
